This baseline applies gradient-boosted trees (the XGBoost library) to the
DeepCell Types evaluation harness using mean per-channel marker
intensities as features. There is no paper-specific implementation being
adapted; XGBoost is a standard machine-learning method.

XGBoost is distributed separately as ``xgboost`` on PyPI under the
Apache License 2.0.

